g.text: US1004 - As Customer Manager, I want to edit a job opening.
asks to edit a job opening
show the list of all job openings and request the selection of one
Shows Mode list (remote, hybrid, onsite...) and asks to select one
Shows Contract Types list (full-time, part-time,...) and asks to select one
Requests Address Data (street, city, state, zip-code)
Shows list of the registered Requirement Specifications and asks to select one
Shows list of the registered Interview Models and asks to select one
